164
00:12:45.680 --> 00:12:47.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Inconsciente.

165
00:12:48.120 --> 00:12:50.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Caprichosa, superficial, egoísta.

166
00:12:52.600 --> 00:12:53.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
¿Cómo te defines tú?

167
00:12:58.000 --> 00:13:00.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
