00:13:43.840 --> 00:13:44.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
¿Llevo mucho rato?

177
00:13:45.880 --> 00:13:46.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.green>No lo sé.</c.green>

178
00:13:48.400 --> 00:13:51.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
La primera vez
que me acuesto con una tía

179
00:13:51.320 --> 00:13:52.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
