217
00:17:08.120 --> 00:17:09.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
¡Espera, joder, Berlín!

218
00:17:10.560 --> 00:17:13.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
¡Escúchame, para, para, para, para,
tienes razón!

219
00:17:14.520 --> 00:17:15.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Tienes razón.

220
