255
00:19:10.880 --> 00:19:15.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.yellow>Yo, en cambio, voy supersencilla.</c.yellow>
Si por eso te lo digo...

256
00:19:15.480 --> 00:19:18.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.yellow>A ver, ¿dónde vamos?</c.yellow>
A la verbena.

257
00:19:18.080 --> 00:19:20.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.yellow>Entonces,</c.yellow>
<c.yellow>tendrás que ir de putón...</c.yellow>

