00:19:20.760 --> 00:19:21.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
(AMBAS) Verbenero.

259
00:19:23.200 --> 00:19:25.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
