291
00:21:16.840 --> 00:21:18.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.yellow>No me reconociera.</c.yellow>

292
00:21:20.600 --> 00:21:22.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.yellow>Porque creía que era...</c.yellow>

293
00:21:23.000 --> 00:21:24.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.yellow>diferente,</c.yellow>

294
00:21:25.760 --> 00:21:28.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.yellow>pero en realidad</c.yellow>
