295
00:21:29.720 --> 00:21:31.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.yellow>Y que se cansa de todo.</c.yellow>

296
00:21:33.840 --> 00:21:35.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.yellow>Y que no hace feliz a la gente.</c.yellow>

297
00:21:39.840 --> 00:21:41.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.yellow>Y no me gusta cómo soy.</c.yellow>

298
00:21:44.600 --> 00:21:47.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.yellow>Y tampoco me gusta este libro</c.yellow>
