300
00:21:49.040 --> 00:21:50.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.yellow>Dice que soy una mujer tóxica.</c.yellow>

301
00:21:54.280 --> 00:21:58.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Si estás intentando dejarme,
alejarte o algo por el estilo,

302
00:21:58.960 --> 00:22:00.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ni lo intentes.

303
00:22:03.360 --> 00:22:04.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.yellow>Río, tío...</c.yellow>

304
00:22:07.640 --> 00:22:08.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.yellow>Soy tierra quemada.</c.yellow>

305
00:22:11.040 --> 00:22:12.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.yellow>Peor.</c.yellow>

306
00:22:12.920 --> 00:22:15.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.yellow>Soy un puto bidón de gasolina</c.yellow>
<c.yellow>y una cerilla.</c.yellow>

307
00:22:16.560 --> 00:22:18.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Pues a mí me encantan las hogueras.

308
00:22:19.280 --> 00:22:21.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Y si eres tóxica, pues me mareo.

309
00:22:21.920 --> 00:22:24.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
