310
00:22:25.720 --> 00:22:26.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Mira.

311
00:22:29.560 --> 00:22:31.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Cuando yo te veo
al otro lado del museo,

312
00:22:31.960 --> 00:22:33.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
me dan ganas de llorar...

313
00:22:34.800 --> 00:22:36.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
por el simple hecho
de estar contigo.

314
00:22:38.600 --> 00:22:40.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Y follamos
y floto por la habitación.

315
00:22:50.160 --> 00:22:51.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yo ya sé que me vas a dejar.

316
00:22:53.680 --> 00:22:55.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
