349
00:25:43.120 --> 00:25:44.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
-No escuché nada.

350
00:25:45.360 --> 00:25:47.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
