Id corriendo a la unidad.

357
00:26:08.320 --> 00:26:09.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
-Central, efectivamente,

358
00:26:09.640 --> 00:26:11.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
"han entrado,
pero ya no hay nadie".

359
00:26:11.320 --> 00:26:14.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
