362
00:26:28.320 --> 00:26:29.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
¡Denver!

363
00:26:33.160 --> 00:26:34.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
¿Denver?

364
00:26:37.760 --> 00:26:38.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Denver.

365
00:26:40.480 --> 00:26:43.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Te estaba buscando.
-Aquí me tienes.

366
00:26:49.000 --> 00:26:50.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
-Resulta que...

367
00:26:51.000 --> 00:26:53.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
mi cara no deja de salir
en los informativos.

368
00:26:54.720 --> 00:26:56.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
