372
00:27:12.360 --> 00:27:14.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Un botón de mi chaqueta.

373
00:27:14.720 --> 00:27:16.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
