376
00:27:21.480 --> 00:27:24.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Un coche en el que, por cierto,
yo, estoy seguro, no...

377
00:27:25.480 --> 00:27:26.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
No me subí jamás.

378
00:27:27.480 --> 00:27:29.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
