379
00:27:29.720 --> 00:27:30.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
-No lo sé.

380
00:27:30.800 --> 00:27:32.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Sí que lo sabes.
-No lo sé.

381
00:27:32.520 --> 00:27:34.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
-Que me acabas de joder la vida.

382
00:27:34.360 --> 00:27:35.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
-Venga.

383
00:27:36.360 --> 00:27:37.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
-¿Qué hago contigo?

384
00:27:37.720 --> 00:27:38.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
-Berlín.

385
00:27:40.760 --> 00:27:42.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Lo siento, tío,
no me di cuenta del puto botón.

386
00:27:43.200 --> 00:27:46.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
