-¿15 millones?

388
00:27:47.960 --> 00:27:49.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
-15 millones, no me jodas.

389
00:27:49.840 --> 00:27:52.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
