-Te lo firmo si quieres, sí.

391
00:27:56.680 --> 00:27:58.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-¿Por un botón?
-Por un botón.

392
00:27:59.360 --> 00:28:01.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
