400
00:28:25.760 --> 00:28:26.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
-Berlín.

401
00:28:27.240 --> 00:28:29.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
-Sí... Chist.

